rivacy notice The US Olympic and Paralympic Committee (USOPC) has raised the bar on mental health services in sport, Jess Bartley, the senior director of psychological services at the USOPC, said on Monday.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"The US Olympic and Paralympic Committee\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"USOPC\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health services\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"Jess Bartley\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"the senior director\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological services\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the USOPC\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once seen as taboo in the hard-charging world of elite sports, the topic of mental health was thrust to the fore thanks in part to American gymnastSimone Biles, who rewrote the playbook onathlete wellness at the Tokyo Gamesthree years ago.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999977958749885, \"rank\": 9.781114893102138e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"taboo\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard-charging world\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sports\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"the topic\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the fore thanks\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the playbook onathlete wellness\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There does not have to be anything wrong with you to focus on your mental health,\\\" said Bartley.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"your mental health\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"Bartley\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have just really, really improved, the level of service, the quality of service, that all of these athletes can get when it comes to mental health.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I do not think we are done.\\\"\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The USOPC had adopted a more proactive approach to athletes' mental health at the Beijing Games,learning lessons from Bilesand emphasising crisis prevention and maintenance.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The USOPC\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"a more proactive approach\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' mental health\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Games\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"lessons\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"Bilesand\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"crisis prevention\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"maintenance\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sleep hygiene has become a major focus going into this summer's Paris Games, said Bartley, who joined the USOPC in a newly created position in 2020.\